com.nestedbird.models.core.Base

Class BaseController<E extends BaseEntity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nestedbird.models.core.Base.BaseController<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - What type of base entity is this
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArtistController, EventController, EventTimeController, LocationController, MediumController, PrivilegeController, RoleController, ScannedPageController, SongController, TagController, UserController

    public abstract class BaseController<E extends BaseEntity>
extends java.lang.Object
    The Base Controller contains common endpoints for all BaseEntities. To use the Base Controller a BaseEntities controller needs to extend it The endpoints are relative to the url of the base entities controller
